{"tid":686653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴關愛座飛脫　1人受傷","createTime":"2018-06-01T13:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T06:09:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":798,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"59bf97ba75aaf29ad63b0f1e607dc0bbe1ec1df6","tid":686653,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180601/s00001/51ed2eebd76c3ab0d4a310d503056044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180601%2Fs00001%2F51ed2eebd76c3ab0d4a310d503056044.jpg&h=0a3a9b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴一輛由長沙灣開出的214線九巴，今日下午1時左右，駛至龍翔道近豐力樓時，巴士下層左方近尾閘的關愛座，突然向右傾側，一名乘客受傷。據網傳圖片所見，整個座位向右倒在通道上，黃色扶手欄杆亦一同飛脫。<br />\n<br />\n事後車長已報警，受傷乘客已送往醫院治理。九巴表示關注事件，並向傷者致以慰問。至於意外原因，九巴指仍在調查中。"},{"pid":"d038378f6652abd01868107edbe96f4f57282cdf","tid":686653,"uid":35930,"like":68,"dislike":5,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"又要多謝黨"},{"pid":"86ff971847f3c5838c9a7f061532af4540251093","tid":686653,"uid":20933,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180601/s00001/51eadf21cbc698c92f09f7679980fc6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180601%2Fs00001%2F51eadf21cbc698c92f09f7679980fc6c.jpg&h=8b91a007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180601/s00001/51ebe5b6de8a048efb3c47973c44dd37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180601%2Fs00001%2F51ebe5b6de8a048efb3c47973c44dd37.jpg&h=f69d4212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83584a2cc4bb93622f46054196b009d0b27a61a3","tid":686653,"uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180601/s00001/1527857365681?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.co